            <title>[LU-3813] Interop 2.4&lt;-&gt;2.5 failure on test suite sanity test_102b: stripe count 6 != 7</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3813</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/bfe9f440-09ec-11e3-ad93-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/bfe9f440-09ec-11e3-ad93-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_102b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;stripe count 6 != 7&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 102b&lt;/p&gt;</description>
